publisher			Matthew Brown							
publish_time	 2014年9月1日		
desc_long							评测						“...the sense of artistry behind the crafting of the puzzles, puts this a level above.”Rock Paper Shotgun												关于这款游戏							Hexcells Infinite is the third game in the series of ambient logic puzzle games.It includes a new set of 36 puzzles as well as a random puzzle generator and now supports mid-level saving and cross platform cloud saves.The level generator uses an 8 digit seed number to generate each puzzle so they can easily be shared.						
